{"word":"H1391 - גִּבְעֹון - Gibʻôwn - ghib-ohn' - Gibeon","slug":"H1391","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גִּבְעֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Gibʻôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ghib-ohn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Gibeon"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>גּבעון</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>gib‛ôn</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ghib-ohn'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Gibeon = \"hill city\" <ol><li>a Levitical city of Benjamin, modern 'el-Jib', which lies 5 miles or 8 kilometers from Jerusalem</li></ol> <p />Origin: from the same as <a href=\"#/H1387\">H1387</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1375\">H1375</a>, <a href=\"#/H1387\">H1387</a>, <a href=\"#/H1388\">H1388</a>, <a href=\"#/H1389\">H1389</a>, <a href=\"#/H1390\">H1390</a>, <a href=\"#/H1392\">H1392</a>, <a href=\"#/H1393\">H1393</a>, <a href=\"#/H1394\">H1394</a>, <a href=\"#/H1395\">H1395</a>, <a href=\"#/H25\">H25</a>, <a href=\"#/H4021\">H4021</a>"}]}